2. Embedding Atlas (UMAP / NNDescent Rust crates)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Rust crates under `packages/dashql-umap/` (`umap`, `nndescent`, `umap-wasm`)
are vendored from Apple's Embedding Atlas project
(https://github.com/apple/embedding-atlas), specifically `packages/umap/{umap,
nndescent,umap-wasm}`. They are compiled to WebAssembly for the client-side UMAP
projection behind `VISUALIZE ... USING umap`, including the GPU (`wgpu`
→ WebGPU) feature and its sources/shaders (`gpu.rs`, `nn_descent_gpu.rs`,
`gpu_optimize.rs`, `**/shaders/*.wgsl`). All files retain their original
`// Copyright (c) 2025 Apple Inc. Licensed under MIT License.` headers. Licensed
under the same MIT License as section 1 (Copyright (c) 2025 Apple Inc.).

